        pig1 dies           x :) :)
        pig1 + pig2 dies    x  x :)
        pig1 + pig3 dies    x :) x
        pig2 dies           :) x :)
        pig2 + pig3 dies    :) x x
        pig3 dies           :) :)x
        pig3 + pig1 + pig2 dies
        no pigs die (must be bucket not tested)
        There are 8 possibilities each step given 3 pigs (2^3)
          each possibility corresponds to a bucket that can be identified
		So each pig still has the same possible outcomes (steps + 1) but now for each of those outcomes, there are 2^p additional outcomes
        SO, for k steps and where p is for number of pigs, the buckets (possible combos - b) are:
          b = (k+1)^p

		We need to solve for p where b => the buckets param 
  */

  let k = Math.ceil(minutesToTest / minutesToDie); // max number of steps the can be taken
  let total = 1;
  let res = 0;
  while (total < buckets) {
    total = total * (k + 1); // each pig represents this increase in possible combos       
    res++;
  }

  return res;
};

